<i>1...</i>

546
00:31:03,029 --> 00:31:03,943
<i>Nula.</i>

547
00:31:04,155 --> 00:31:06,362
<i>Hjustone,
ovde "Jarac 1".</i>

548
00:31:08,035 --> 00:31:09,198
<i>Sleteli smo.</i>

549
00:31:40,447 --> 00:31:43,484
<i>- Da?
- Potpredsednik Prajs na vezi.</i>

550
00:31:46,621 --> 00:31:47,617
Halo.

551
00:31:48,832 --> 00:31:50,410
Zdravo, g. potpredsedniče.

552
00:31:52,002 --> 00:31:53,580
Da, divno, zar ne?

553
00:31:54,422 --> 00:31:56,414
Trenutak ponosa
za sve Amerikance.

554
00:31:58,551 --> 00:32:01,339
Poručite predsedniku da je to
vrlo dražesno od njega.

555
00:32:01,555 --> 00:32:03,429
Cenim to, zaista.

556
00:32:05,059 --> 00:32:06,055
Hvala vam.

557
00:32:06,519 --> 00:32:08,642
Pozdravite svoju
divnu suprugu.

558
00:32:09,856 --> 00:32:10,770
Da.

559
00:32:11,608 --> 00:32:12,604
Doviðenja.

560
00:32:15,738 --> 00:32:16,936
Degen.

561
00:32:28,544 --> 00:32:30,755
Doktore, imate li
trenutak vremena?

562
00:32:30,755 --> 00:32:32,629
Naravno, ima li
nekih problema?

563
00:32:32,799 --> 00:32:35,207
Nešto mi nikako nije jasno.

564
00:32:35,552 --> 00:32:36,548
A šta to?

565
00:32:37,805 --> 00:32:40,808
Nisam baš siguran,
u vezi sa očitavanjima.

566
00:32:40,808 --> 00:32:45,186
Odavno sam to pomenuo dr Bergenu,
a on je rekao da je to do konzole.

567
00:32:45,814 --> 00:32:47,356
Voleo bih da vi pogledate.

568
00:32:48,108 --> 00:32:51,237
- Koja je to konzola?
- Telemetrija, 36.

569
00:32:51,237 --> 00:32:55,283
O, da, dr Bergen mi je rekao.
Popravili smo to.

570
00:32:55,283 --> 00:32:56,994
Znam, gospodine, samo...

571
00:32:56,994 --> 00:32:58,737
I dalje dobijam iste podatke.

572
00:32:59,330 --> 00:33:01,239
Kakve?

573
00:33:01,874 --> 00:33:05,629
Pokrenuo sam moj sopstveni
program radi provere

574
00:33:05,629 --> 00:33:07,538
i dobio drugačija očitavanja.

575
00:33:08,632 --> 00:33:10,257
Vaš sopstveni program?

576
00:33:11,469 --> 00:33:12,548
Da, gospodine,

577
00:33:14,013 --> 00:33:15,258
i...

578
00:33:15,765 --> 00:33:17,308
Mislim da nije
do konzole.

579
00:33:19,645 --> 00:33:22,481
Ništa, isključićemo je i
proveriti je li popravljena.

580
00:33:22,481 --> 00:33:25,151
Hvala ti, Eliote, sto
si mi skrenuo pažnju na ovo.

581
00:33:29,072 --> 00:33:30,353
Nema na čemu.

582
00:33:43,464 --> 00:33:45,920
<i>Ovde Pol Kaningem,
Kontrola "Jarca".</i>

583
00:33:46,134 --> 00:33:49,220
<i>Direktor leta savetuje
da posada modula dobije dozvolu</i>

584
00:33:49,220 --> 00:33:51,598
<i>za prvi izlazak
na površinu Marsa.</i>

585
00:33:51,598 --> 00:33:54,727
<i>S obzirom da zbog vremenskog kašnjenja
nije mogucah konverzacija,</i>

586
00:33:54,727 --> 00:33:56,729
<i>posada ima ranije
snimljenu poruku</i>

587
00:33:56,729 --> 00:33:58,982
<i>od predsednika.</i>

588
00:33:58,982 --> 00:34:00,642
<i>Ovde Kontrola "Jarca".</i>

589
00:34:00,901 --> 00:34:02,694
<i>Hjustone, uključujemo
kameru.</i>

590
00:34:02,694 --> 00:34:03,476
<i>Primljeno, "Jarče".</i>

591
00:34:06,449 --> 00:34:08,489
<i>Hjustone, trebalo bi
da sada imate sliku.</i>

592
00:34:08,910 --> 00:34:11,995
<i>- Imamo vrlo dobru sliku.
- Ja sam van kabine.</i>

593
00:34:13,498 --> 00:34:15,207
<i>Na stepenicama.</i>

594
00:34:15,918 --> 00:34:17,710
<i>Zaštitno odelo je ispravno.</i>

595
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:20,625
<i>Stepenice su stabilne.
Tri stepenika do tla.</i>

596
00:34:22,884 --> 00:34:24,628
<i>Još dva stepenika.</i>

597
00:34:28,307 --> 00:34:29,932
<i>Na poslednjem sam stepeniku.</i>

598
00:34:32,312 --> 00:34:35,099
<i>Sada ću spustiti nogu
na površinu.</i>

599
00:34:36,942 --> 00:34:38,187
Spremi usporeni snimak.

600
00:34:38,903 --> 00:34:40,397
<i>Pravim ovaj korak</i>

601
00:34:40,780 --> 00:34:42,440
<i>na putu mira</i>

602
00:34:43,116 --> 00:34:44,694
<i>za celo covečanstvo.</i>

603
00:34:45,160 --> 00:34:46,156
Uspori snimak!

604
00:34:52,210 --> 00:34:54,666
<i>Hjustone, na površini sam.</i>

605
00:34:55,046 --> 00:34:56,920
Primljeno, "Jarce".

606
00:34:57,174 --> 00:34:58,965
<i>Sada počinjem sa šetnjom.</i>

607
00:35:00,845 --> 00:35:05,009
<i>Površina je čvrsta.
Vidljivost dobra.</i>

608
00:35:05,433 --> 00:35:07,011
<i>Sada idem prema kameri.</i>

609
00:35:09,313 --> 00:35:10,724
<i>Postolje je stabilno.</i>

610
00:35:12,483 --> 00:35:14,441
<i>Površina je prasnjava.</i>

611
00:35:15,153 --> 00:35:16,861
<i>Podižem kameru.</i>

612
00:35:17,906 --> 00:35:19,365
<i>Uzeo sam kameru.</i>

613
00:35:20,325 --> 00:35:22,484
<i>Neko vreme
slika će podrhtavati.</i>

614
